## Install Obsidian
You can install Obsidian from [here](https://obsidian.md/).

## How to use Obsidian
We can use Obsidian as a personal knowledge management system.
For more information, see [here](https://velog.io/@ji-one/9v7aqpip).

I think it is a good tool to manage personal TODO list. It seems like a application of Notion and Figma.
You can make daily TODO list and manage it like below.

